quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  2,177,"Dewal ngal wonaali fewtiЕӢgol geece mon Й—en Й“aЕӢnge fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange. Ko woni tun dewal ngal: ko on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, e Malaa'ika en, e Deftere nden, e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en; o okki jawdi -e hoore yiЙ—ugol ndi- joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e Й“illiiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“ii hoore-laawol, e Й“en torotooЙ“e, e fii rinЙ—inngol daaЙ—e; o niiЙ“ni juulde, o totti asakal, e Й“en hunnooЙ“e aadondiral maЙ“Й“e si Й“e haldidaama, e Й“en muГұГұitooЙ“e ka baasi e ka lorra, e fewndo gowole. Ko Й“en ngoni goonguЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en kadi ngoni gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,178,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e,njottiigu farlaama e mo'on:dimo sabu dimo, jeyaaЙ—o sabu jeyaaЙ—o,deyel sabu deyel.Kala ya'fanaaЙ—o goЙ—Й—um e musiЙ—Й—o makko,ko jokkitirogol no moЖҙЖҙiri tottira e makko no moЖҙЖҙiri.ЖҠum Й—oo ko hoynaneede immorde e Joomi mo'on e yurmeende.Kala on jaggituЙ—o Й“aawo Й—u'um,no woodani mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  2,179,"No woodani on ka njottiigu nguurdam, yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqilaaji. Belajo'o on wonay gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,180,"Farlaama e mo'on:si maayde nden arii e mo'on,si o accii jawle: wasiyanagol jibinЙ“e mo Й“en,e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri.Ko hannduyee e dow gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  2,181,"Kala on waylituЙ—o Й—um Й“aawo o nannde, pellet bakkaatu mun on ko Й“en waylituЙ“e fawii. Allah ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,182,"On mo huli ooГұaare immorde e wasiyiiЙ—o maa bakkaatu o moЖҙЖҙini hakkunde maЙ“Й“e,bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Pellet Alla ko Yawtanoowo YurmotooЙ—o"
  2,183,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, koorka kan farlaama e mo'on wano ka farliranoo e Й“en adinooЙ“e on, Й“elajo'o laatoЙ—on gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,184,"Г‘alЙ—i limtaaЙ—i. Kala e mo'on laatiiЙ—o nawnuЙ—o maa e hoore-jahal: ko limtugol ГұalЙ—i goo. No fawii Й“en haЙ—tanЙ“e ka, Гұammingol Й“iliiЙ—o. Kala on gattuЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere Й—um no moЖҙЖҙani mo. Ko nde hooroton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si wonii hiЙ—on nganndi"
  2,185,"Lewru koorka ndun, ndu Alqur'aanaare nden jippinaa e mu'un, ko ndu peewal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en e Й“angannduyeeji immorde e peewal e serndugol. On e mo'on seediiЙ—o lewru ndun, yo o hooru ndu. On tawЙ—o no nawni maa himo e hoore-jahal, ko limtugol e ГұalЙ—i goo. Alla no Faandanii on neweende O Faandanaaki on saЙ—teende; e fii yo on timmin limoore nden e no mawniniro Alla kon ko O Fewni on, belajo'o on jaarnay Mo"
  2,186,"Si jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en lamndike lan fii Am, hary Min: Ko Mi ЖҒaЙ—iiЙ—o. MiЙ—o Jaabina toraare torotooЙ—o si o torike Lam. Yo Й“e nooto Lam, e yo Й“e gomЙ—inam, belajo'o Й“e feeway"
  2,187,"Daginanaama on jemma koorka kan yiidugol e rewЙ“e mon Й“en. Ko Й“e koltu mo'on ko on koltu maЙ“Й“e. Alla Anndii wonde on laatinoke jaЕӢfotooЙ“e ko*e-mon,O JaЙ“ani on tuubuubuyee O Ya'fii on.Jooni non,soccondiree e maЙ“Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“on ko Alla Winndani on.Г‘aamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol Й“aЕӢngirana on Й“alewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e maЙ“Й“e hara ko on ufniiЙ“e ka juulirЙ—e.ЖҠum ko keeri Allah, wata on Й“aЙ—to Й—i.Ko wano nii Allaahu On ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta yimЙ“e Й“en aayeeje Makko Й—en,belajo'o Й“e wona gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,188,"Wata on Гұaamir jawle mon Й—en hakkundeeji mo'on e hoore mehre, werloron Й—e e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en fii yo fedde goo Гұaamira e jawle yimЙ“e Й“en bakkaatu, hara hiЙ—on nganndi"